      <title>機械需求趨於穩定，卡特彼勒和迪爾庫存成為焦點</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/caterpillar-deere-inventories-focus-machinery-demand-plateaus-2024-04-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡特彼勒、迪爾和凱斯紐荷蘭工業集團將在未來幾週內公佈季度業績，屆時設備庫存將成為焦點，因為投資者正在等待該行業預計疲軟的一年的需求線索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/caterpillar-deere-inventories-focus-machinery-demand-plateaus-2024-04-24/</guid>
